<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Channel Ten has announced The Masked Singer US is coming to Australian television in October.</p>

<p>On Friday, the network shared a promotional photo of the judges of the US version of the show to Instagram.</p>

<p>'Keen for more Masked Singer? We've got you covered! The Masked Singer US is heading to 10 play from Thursday October 1st,' the captioned read.</p>

<p>Grab the popcorn! Network Ten announced The Masked Singer US is coming to Australian TV. Pictured Ken Jeong, Nicole Scherzinger, Nick Cannon, Jenny McCarthy and Robin Thicke</p>

<p>In the photo, judges Robin Thicke, Jenny McCarthy, Ken Jeong, Nicole Scherzinger, and host Nick Cannon posed alongside one another.</p>

<p>Meanwhile, the grand finale episode of The Masked Singer Australia took place on Monday night and Bushranger was crowned the winner.</p>

<p>The celebrity inside the costume was revealed to be Neighbours actress Bonnie Anderson, 25. </p>

<p>Finale: This comes after the grand finale episode of The Masked Singer Australia took place on Monday night. Pictured judge Jackie O Henderson</p>

<p>Emerging from the costume, actress Bonnie said she was excited to return to singing after a stint on television.  </p>

<p>'I haven't really been singing for a while, you know. Neighbours has kind of taken a lot of my time, so it has kind of sparked up a little bit of fire in me,' she said. </p>

<p>Bonnie added that she struggled to keep her identity hidden from friends and family.</p>

<p>Revealed! Bushranger was crowned the winner and the celebrity inside the costume was finally revealed</p>

<p>'It's very hard to lie on this show, I tell you. All of my family, my friends, all of you watching, were bugging me. </p>

<p>'I'm a terrible liar but I think my acting skills came in to play. It's a good feeling and I can't believe that I won this thing!' she concluded excitedly. </p>

<p>Continuing her winning streak, judge Dannii Minogue yet again guessed right, after disagreeing with Dave Hughes who was long convinced it was Jessica Mauboy. </p>

<p>It's her! It was none other than Neighbours actress, Bonnie Anderson (pictured)</p>
